# Title:
Travel Cost Calculator Program

# Description:
Experience seamless trip planning with our Travel Cost Calculator Program! This online tool allows users to effortlessly 
estimate their total travel expenses by inputting destination preferences, the number of nights to spend in a hotel, 
and the desired duration for car rental. The program employs a user-friendly interface to collect and process this information, 
delivering a comprehensive breakdown of costs including plane fare, hotel accommodation, and car rental fees. 
Whether you're dreaming of a getaway to Italy, Nigeria, South Africa, the United Kingdom, or Canada, our program 
ensures accurate cost estimates for your entire holiday. Simplify your travel budgeting with this intuitive 
and efficient tool, making your trip-planning process both enjoyable and stress-free. Try it now and embark on your 
next adventure with confidence!
